{"id":"811373333859926016","type":"text","timestamp":1773785909,"post_url":"https://www.tumblr.com/blog/view/goodtransgirl/811373333859926016","is_reblog":true,"added_content":false,"tags":[],"reblog_ready":false,"body":"<p><a class=\"tumblr_blog\" href=\"https://whimsy-flags.tumblr.com/post/811164652043141120/hey-you-uh-coming-to-the-party-no-no-shh\">whimsy-flags</a>:</p><blockquote><p>Hey, you uh&hellip; <i>coming to the party? </i></p><p>No no, SHH DUDE! Brutus said we were calling it a&hellip; y'know, a <i>party! </i>Cause it&rsquo;s a <i>surprise party, </i>and we can&rsquo;t have the big guy finding out early, yeah? </p><p>So, did you uh&hellip; bring any <i>gifts? </i></p><p>&hellip; you forgot your <i>fucking <b>knife?! </b></i></p><p><i>GIFT</i>, yeah, I KNOW! </p><p>Okay&hellip; okay. </p><p>Here, fucking&hellip; I brought extras. </p><p><br/></p><div class=\"npf_row\"><figure class=\"tmblr-full\" data-orig-height=\"800\" data-orig-width=\"800\"><img src=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/673539719a62f81ecbd5fc702aaca9a0/dfc2718293532530-85/s640x960/208d51365c5f643a2e365b97df0a12a3fdaad76b.png\" data-orig-height=\"800\" data-orig-width=\"800\" srcset=\"https://64.media.tumblr.com/673539719a62f81ecbd5fc702aaca9a0/dfc2718293532530-85/s75x75_c1/c988914e5d3b34c7e4654fdec7e40206006805bc.png 75w, https://64.media.tumblr.com/673539719a62f81ecbd5fc702aaca9a0/dfc2718293532530-85/s100x200/98413ce4cc77a961595c11bd1d94b2c6","trail":[{"blog":{"name":"whimsy-flags"},"post":{"id":"811164652043141120"}}],"baseline_notes":7693,"baseline_ts":1774705101.464}